# Roasted White Bean and Tomato Pasta

Based on [https://cooking.nytimes.com/recipes/1024062-roasted-white-bean-and-tomato-pasta](https://cooking.nytimes.com/recipes/1024062-roasted-white-bean-and-tomato-pasta) ([wayback](http://web.archive.org/web/20251122150637/https://cooking.nytimes.com/recipes/1024062-roasted-white-bean-and-tomato-pasta))

